data.description: Welcome to this charming, meticulously maintained, single-level home right in the heart of Boise on over a quarter acre with no CCRs/HOA! This adorable residence offers a spacious layout and tons of great features, including TWO living rooms and a generous backyard with a covered patio that's perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. The large yard boasts ample room for relaxation and play and also includes convenient RV parking, dedicated garden space and storage shed. This home offers the best of both worlds - a serene suburban oasis while still being in close proximity to schools, restaurants, city parks/pools, freeway, downtown and more.
